Name: Toilet Paper Unleashed
About the game: Toilet Paper Unleashed is here. Explore two levels of toilet paper searching madness. Run and jump to find all 8 rolls of golden toilet paper in distinct environments: Warehouse and Parking Lot with Store. Carefully maneuver the level while avoiding moving menacing shopping carts. Background music and other short stings included. Find all the TP!
